publisher			Tonguç Bodur							
publish_time	 2015年3月12日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							In Drizzlepath you are set on a journey to the top of the Mountain of Fire. This game is what you'd call a "walking simulator". It aims to be an atmospheric, relaxed and enigmatic experience. It was made in CryEngine 3 to achieve an immersive graphic quality. If you enjoy games that are about the experience of discovering of the world around you, you will probably love Drizzlepath.						
title	 Drizzlepath			
